profile:
Proud Recipient of Calgary's 2018 CHBA Renovator of the Year!

Kay 2 Contracting is an Award-winning Custom Home Renovator and Builder serving the greater Calgary and Edmonton areas. We specialize in full scale renovations and Custom Home Builds including home additions, kitchens, bathrooms, interior & structural design. 

Our services include: 

-Interior design 
-Architectural design
-Engineering
-Home Renovations
-Additions 
-Kitchen
-Bathroom
-Basement
-Landscape Construction

profile: APS Landscaping Inc is a full service landscaping contractor specializing in residential and commercial install, lot grading, landscape design and snow removal. Belgard Authorized.
